item.title: Quotables
item.description: Introduction In this post I will collect all the quotes that I find interesting or hold a special meaning to me. I imagine I’ll come back here from time to time to find inspiration and motivation. Hos successus alit: possunt, quia posse videntur. – Publius Vergilius Maro
